description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 5.2 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Residential Dishwashers that are effective as of January 20, 2012. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=dishwash.pr_crit_dishwashers
